                  ></path>
                </svg>
                LinkedIn
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='content-section'>
          <h3>My Background</h3>
          <p>
            With extensive experience in modern web technologies including Angular, Node.js, and
            real-time communication systems, I've dedicated my career to building secure,
            user-friendly applications. My expertise spans frontend development, backend
            architecture, encryption implementation, and database design.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='content-section'>
          <h3>Why Quasar Contact?</h3>
          <p>
            In today's digital landscape, privacy is becoming increasingly rare. I built Quasar
            Contact to address this challenge - creating a messaging platform that puts user privacy
            first, implements true end-to-end encryption, and maintains a zero-knowledge
            architecture. Every technical decision is made with user privacy and security in mind.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='content-section'>
          <h3>Technical Expertise</h3>
          <div class='skills-grid'>
            <div class='skill-category'>
              <h4>Frontend</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Angular 18+</li>
                <li>TypeScript</li>
                <li>RxJS</li>
                <li>Progressive Web Apps</li>
                <li>Web Crypto API</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class='skill-category'>
              <h4>Backend</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Node.js</li>
                <li>Express.js</li>
                <li>Socket.IO</li>
                <li>MongoDB</li>
                <li>JWT Authentication</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class='skill-category'>
              <h4>Security</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>End-to-End Encryption</li>
                <li>Zero-Knowledge Architecture</li>
                <li>GDPR Compliance</li>
                <li>Security Best Practices</li>
                <li>Privacy by Design</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='content-section'>
          <h3>Philosophy</h3>
          <p>I believe that:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Privacy is a fundamental right</strong> - Not a luxury or optional feature
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Security should be transparent</strong> - Users should understand how their data
              is protected
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Technology should empower users</strong> - Not exploit or surveillance them
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Open communication fosters innovation</strong> - Feedback and collaboration improve
              everything
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class='content-section'>
          <h3>Future Vision</h3>
          <p>
            My goal is to continuously improve Quasar Contact based on user feedback and evolving
            security needs. I'm committed to maintaining the highest standards of privacy and
            security while making the platform accessible to users of all technical backgrounds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='contact-section'>
          <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
          <p>
            I'm always open to feedback, suggestions, and discussions about privacy, security, or
            technology in general.
          </p>

          <div class='contact-links'>
            <a href='mailto:artem.turlenko@quasar.contact' class='contact-link'>
